Class LinkedListIndexedCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections.Collection
      • hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections.LinkedListIndexedCollection

  • public class LinkedListIndexedCollection
extends Collection
    Class represents linked list-backed collection of objects. Duplicate elements are allowed, storage of null references is not allowed.

    1.0
    Author:
    Toni Martinčić
